<h1>THE FINDERS: AN EMBEDDABLE SET OF SEARCH SYSTEMS</h1>

<p>The <i>/finder/</i> URLs comprise a subsystem of embeddable search systems. These mirror the functionality of the Find panels in the Desktop and Mobile app, but are designed for use in an IFRAME and embedded within a website.</p>

<h2>TRAIL FINDER</h2>
<div class="indent bottom">

