<p>
This page accepts URL params to set the state of the checkboxes and other elements:
</p>
<ul>
<li><b>difficulty</b>--A comma-joined list of any of these values: <i>Novice</i>, <i>Beginner</i>, <i>Intermediate</i>, <i>Advanced</i>. For example, <i>Novice,Beginner</i> This sets the checkboxes for the acceptable levels of Difficulty.</li>
