<li><b>paved</b>--A text value, any of: <i>Yes</i>, <i>No</i> This sets the Paved selector.</li>
<li><b>reservation</b>--A text value, the name of any reservation, e.g. <i>Huntington Reservation</i> This sets the reservation selector. <b>This must exactly match the name of the reservation, including capitalization and spaces.</b></li>
</ul>

